{"tid":2350810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸大家對嗰啲乜乜乜冇得搞嘅post唔使太認真，用呢班人嘅mindset 其實由反國教開始每次行動都唔使有幻想","createTime":"2021-01-02T15:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T17:32:24.000Z","uid":31215,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9124bd0869d99c5184b23c5fbb0ee54a65fb9a41","tid":2350810,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:36:16.000Z","msg":"你鍾意嘅，每個行動都可以寫一篇文解釋下點解唔會成功<br />\n<br />\n不要對遊行存在太大幻想<br />\n不要對勇武存在太大幻想<br />\n不要對黃色經濟圈存在太大幻想<br />\n不要對國際戰線存在太大幻想<br />\n不要對中共崩潰存在太大幻想<br />\n不要對議會抗爭存在太大幻想<br />\n不要對初選存在太大幻想<br />\n<br />\n屌on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼唔知樣樣都難咩<br />\n咁多年都係明知不可為而為之<br />\n唔使再有咁多人出黎扮智者講乜乜乜好難成功<br />\n根本在座咁多位都知<br />\n但咪又係一樣要做<br />\n真係智者就分析下有乜空間或者可能性破局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856b2726d0cd5a21379d6bf7b27b36eb3f680dbf","tid":2350810,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d57d39ca62129daa9fe22feafd63b39d8efff6d","tid":2350810,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18eebfd959a2bf5b0f2186e3cbee8cfd83cda390","tid":2350810,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d57d39ca62129daa9fe22feafd63b39d8efff6d","tid":2350810,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=